fr.gouv.vitam.tools.sedalib.core

Interface DataObject

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BinaryDataObject, DataObjectGroup, PhysicalDataObject

    public interface DataObject
    The Interface DataObject.

    Interface for SEDA elements BinaryDataObject, PhysicalDataObject and DataObjectGroup that can be managed the same way in export and import for edition, and linked to ArchiveUnit.
